  "prompt": "What is the best time to visit Kanniyakumari?",
  "response": "The best time to visit Kanyakumari, located at the southern tip of India, is from October to March. During these months, the weather is generally pleasant and comfortable, with lower humidity and cooler temperatures, making it ideal for sightseeing and outdoor activities. Particularly, December to February is considered the peak tourist season due to the favorable climate.\n\nIf you prefer to avoid the crowds, visiting in October or November can be a good option, as the weather is still pleasant but the tourist influx is lower. Additionally, it's wise to avoid the monsoon months (June to September), as heavy rainfall can disrupt travel plans and outdoor activities.",
